s on such sample. The estimated\nconcentration parameter then lies in the range 1.5 < c < 14 and the anisotropy\nparameter in the range -1.1 < \\beta < 0.5 at the 95 percent confidence level.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2005 14:21:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2005 10:55:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
